message.entry: Expected occupancy value to be a scalar or a vector with number of columns equal to number of points.
Coordinate position outside world dimensions. The minimum and maximum world limits are [{0} {1}] in X direction, [{2} {3}] in Y direction and [{4} {5}] in Z direction.
The visualization function ''{0}'' is not supported in code generation.
Expected file extension to be ".bt" or ".ot" but found "{0}".
Directions must be a N-by-2 or N-by-3 matrix.
N-by-3 Direction matrix contains all zero rows. Use directional vector that contains non-zero elements.
MaxRange must be either -1 or a positive finite scalar value.
